msgid ""
"Published [JSON "
"Schemas](https://github.com/Nastwinns/hawser/tree/main/schemas) and thin "
"[bindings](https://github.com/Nastwinns/hawser/tree/main/bindings) (Python, "
"Go) make it trivial; see the curated "
"[AWESOME-HAW-PLUGINS](https://github.com/Nastwinns/hawser/blob/main/AWESOME-HAW-PLUGINS.md) "
"list."
msgstr ""

#: ./index.md:77
msgid "Distribute & install"
msgstr ""

#: ./index.md:79
msgid ""
"`haw` ships as a single static binary. Install via crates.io, Homebrew, "
"Scoop, AUR, Nix, `.deb`/`.rpm`, Docker, or a signed prebuilt archive — every "
"release carries a `.sha256` checksum and a keyless **cosign** signature. "
"Fleet artifacts publish to private registries (Nexus, Artifactory, GitLab, "
"Bitbucket) via `haw publish`."
msgstr ""

