#: ./index.md:90
msgid "Security"
msgstr ""

#: ./index.md:92
msgid ""
"`haw` runs code declared in the manifest and binaries on your `PATH` — treat "
"both as trusted inputs. The crate is `#![forbid(unsafe_code)]`, HTTPS is "
"rustls-only, actions are SHA-pinned, releases are cosign-signed, and `cargo "
"audit`/`cargo deny` gate every push. Read the full **[trust "
"model](SECURITY.md)**."
msgstr ""

