#: ./learn/04-the-tui-cockpit.md:87 ./learn/04-the-tui-cockpit.md:118
#: ./learn/04-the-tui-cockpit.md:151 ./CLI-DESIGN.md:100 ./CLI-DESIGN.md:117
#: ./CLI-DESIGN.md:132 ./CLI-DESIGN.md:151 ./CLI-DESIGN.md:172
