msgstr ""

#: ./learn/07-going-to-production.md:3
msgid ""
"You can compose a fleet, work across it, ship changesets, build and test it. "
"This final chapter is about doing all of that _for real_ — safely, in CI, "
"with an audit trail — and about the one extensibility escape hatch that ties "
"the governance features together: plugins. It's the difference between a "
"neat local tool and something you trust to gate releases."
msgstr ""

#: ./learn/07-going-to-production.md:11
msgid ""
"_From a neat local tool to something you trust to gate releases — let's "
"launch._"
msgstr ""

#: ./learn/07-going-to-production.md:17
