#: ./learn/08-build-a-plugin-mcp.md:105
msgid "the plugin's **standard input (stdin)**."
msgstr ""

#: ./learn/08-build-a-plugin-mcp.md:107
msgid ""
"The content is identical in both. The environment variable is usually easier "
"because reading it never blocks."
msgstr ""

